@mid
subtitle: Middle term solutions aimed at easing the fundamental issues of the economy

- @importban: Implement restrictions on the import of commercial goods to decrease the flow of foreign currency outwards.
- @export: Incentivize Turkish companies through subsidies to sell their goods abroad and bring in fresh cash.
- @stateplanning: Reform the inefficient state corporations.
- @economy_menu: Return to economic planning.

@importban
choose-if: imf_agreement == 0
unavailable-subtitle: We have agreed with the IMF to not pursue state interventions!
subtitle: Slight popularity decrease; Western relations slightly decrease; Exchange Pressure ↓↓; Industrial Production Index ↑; Agricultural Production Index ↑
