Finally we are seeing the Turkish companies abandon their inactive stance and move to the global markets. Our citizens have suffered real much, but the light at the end of the tunnel is now beginning to shine through. Lets hope our citizens will forgive us for prescribing the painful medicine.

With our fundamental reforms, the Turkish economy has begun moving out of its constant crisis state and now has developed resistance to global crises to some extent.
